<i>Paul Hauser's uncle
visits from West Berlin.</i>

1046
02:00:13,240 --> 02:00:19,640
<i>They tell him about the play Hauser and "Lazlo"
want to write for the Republic's 40th anniversary.</i>

1047
02:00:23,480 --> 02:00:27,960
<i>We're expecting detailed information about
the planned anniversary play: content, etc.</i>

1048
02:00:30,440 --> 02:00:32,440
