<i>Georg Dreyman is the author of the
"Spiegel" article, "From someone who's crossed over".</i>

1058
02:01:31,160 --> 02:01:34,320
<i>Accomplices are
journalist Paul Hauser, Karl Warn...</i>

1059
02:01:42,720 --> 02:01:49,560
<i>Based on evidence from Minister Hempf, Christa-Maria Sieland
