1060
02:01:49,760 --> 02:01:52,920
<i>...and brought back to town
on March 11th at 1:50 pm,</i>

1061
02:01:53,080 --> 02:01:56,197
<i>...having confessed the hiding place
of "Lazlo's" documents</i>

1062
02:01:56,286 --> 02:02:00,052
<i>...and accepted the duties
