Then how did she...?

1065
02:02:10,480 --> 02:02:16,800
<i>After an unsuccessful search on Mar. 11th
and the car accident killing informant "Martha"</i>

1066
02:02:17,360 --> 02:02:19,360
<i>...the operational record
of "Lazlo" was discontinued.</i>

